('agilebits-1password', '1Password', '1Password remembers all your passwords for you, and keeps them safe and secure behind the one password that only you know.', 'Office', 'agilebits-1password-icon', 'LibreOffice Writer / ONLYOFFICE', 50, 'https://1password.com/downloads/windows/'),
