('airsquared-blobsaver', 'blobsaver', 'A cross-platform GUI app for saving SHSH blobs using tsschecker.', 'Utilities', 'airsquared-blobsaver-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/airsquared/blobsaver'),
('airtame-airtame', 'Airtame', 'Revolutionize the way you use shared displays with Airtame - the screen platform that connects, informs and engages teams with solutions for hybrid video conferencing, digital signage, and wireless screen sharing.', 'Development', 'airtame-airtame-icon', '', 0, ''),
('airytec-switchoff', 'Airytec Switch Off', 'Shutdown your PC automatically or remotely from any computer or mobile phone', 'Utilities', 'airytec-switchoff-icon', '', 0, ''),
('aiursoft-kahla', 'Kahla', 'Kahla is a cross-platform business messaging app.', 'Utilities', 'aiursoft-kahla-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/AiursoftWeb/Kahla.App'),
('aivarannamaa-thonny', 'Thonny', 'Thonny is a Python IDE meant for learning programming.', 'Development', 'aivarannamaa-thonny-icon', '', 0, 'https://thonny.org'),
('akelpad-akelpad', 'AkelPad', 'An open source editor for plain text. It is designed to be a small and fast.', 'Design', 'akelpad-akelpad-icon', '', 0, 'http://akelpad.sourceforge.net/'),
('alacritty-alacritty', 'Alacritty', 'Alacritty is a modern terminal emulator that comes with sensible defaults, but allows for extensive configuration.
By integrating with other applications, rather than reimplementing their functionality, it manages to provide a flexible set of features with high performance.
The supported platforms currently consist of BSD, Linux, macOS and Windows.', 'Development', 'alacritty-alacritty-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty'),
('albion-online', 'Albion Online', 'Albion Online is the first truly cross-platform MMO experience, available for Windows, Mac, Linux and Android, with all players on one master server in one massive, sprawling world. You choose how your adventure evolves; at home or on the go!', 'Games', 'albion-online-icon', '', 0, 'https://albiononline.com/download'),
('aleab-toastify', 'Toastify', 'Toastify adds global hotkeys and toast notifications to Spotify', 'Utilities', 'aleab-toastify-icon', '', 0, ''),
('alekseyhoffman-sigma-file-manager', 'Sigma file manager', 'Sigma file manager is a free, open-source, quickly evolving, modern file manager (explorer / finder) app for Windows, MacOS, and Linux.', 'Utilities', 'alekseyhoffman-sigma-file-manager-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/aleksey-hoffman/sigma-file-manager'),
('alexkaul-freeter', 'Freeter', 'The smartest way to work on your projects', 'Design', 'alexkaul-freeter-icon', '', 0, 'https://freeter.io'),
('alexredden-g14controlv2', 'G14ControlV2', 'Management Tools for the Zephyrus G14', 'Utilities', 'alexredden-g14controlv2-icon', '', 0, ''),
('alexthuering-dvdstyler', 'DVDStyler', 'DVDStyler is a cross-platform free DVD authoring application for the creation of professional-looking DVDs.
It allows not only burning of video files on DVD that can be played practically on any standalone DVD player, but also creation of individually designed DVD menus.
It is Open Source Software and is completely free.', 'Development', 'alexthuering-dvdstyler-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.dvdstyler.org/en/'),
('alexanderkojevnikov-spek', 'Spek', 'Spek helps to analyse your audio files by showing their spectrogram.', 'Audio', 'alexanderkojevnikov-spek-icon', '', 0, 'http://spek.cc/'),
('alexandrsubbotin-cerebro', 'Cerebro', 'Open-source productivity booster with a brain', 'Utilities', 'alexandrsubbotin-cerebro-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/cerebroapp/cerebro'),
('algoryx-algodoo', 'Algodoo', 'Algodoo is a unique 2D-simulation software from Algoryx Simulation AB. Algodoo is designed in a playful, cartoony manner, making it a perfect tool for creating interactive scenes. Explore physics, build amazing inventions, design cool games or experiment with Algodoo in your science classes. Algodoo encourages students and children’s own creativity, ability and motivation to construct knowledge while having fun. Making it as entertaining as it is educational. Algodoo is also a perfect aid for children to learn and practice physics at home.', 'Games', 'algoryx-algodoo-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.algodoo.com'),
('alibaba-alibabacloudcli', 'Alibaba Cloud CLI', 'Alibaba Cloud Command Line Interface (Alibaba Cloud CLI) is an open source tool built on the Alibaba Cloud SDK for Go. You can use the aliyun command to interact with other Alibaba Cloud services to manage your Alibaba Cloud resources.
Alibaba Cloud CLI can directly access the Alibaba cloud product OpenAPI. You can manage and maintain your own Alibaba Cloud resources by developing the shell script based on Alibaba Cloud CLI. Make sure that you have activated the cloud product you want to use and understand the API usage of the product.', 'Development', 'alibaba-alibabacloudcli-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/alibaba-cloud-cli'),
('alibaba-dingtalk', 'DingTalk', 'DingTalk is an intelligent working platform created by Alibaba Group to support tens of millions of enterprises to achieve higher working efficiency with the new digitalized working method.', 'Development', 'alibaba-dingtalk-icon', '', 0, 'https://page.dingtalk.com/wow/dingtalk/act/en-download'),
('alibaba-dingtalk-lite', 'DingTalk Lite', 'DingTalk is an intelligent working platform created by Alibaba Group to support tens of millions of enterprises to achieve higher working efficiency with the new digitalized working method.', 'Development', 'alibaba-dingtalk-lite-icon', '', 0, 'https://page.dingtalk.com/wow/dingtalk/act/en-download'),
('alibaba-lightproxy', 'LightProxy', 'LightProxy is an open-source web debugging proxy alternative to Charles, which is based on whistle & Electron.', 'Utilities', 'alibaba-lightproxy-icon', '', 0, 'https://lightproxy.org/'),
('alibaba-teambition', 'Teambition', 'Teambition is a team collaboration tool by Alibaba that promotes collaboration in enterprise and team through visual management of projects and tasks, making it simple, relaxing and enjoyable. It is suitable for various types of teams such as product, R&D, design, marketing, operation, sales, HR, etc.', 'Design', 'alibaba-teambition-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.teambition.com/apps/'),
('alist-alist', 'Alist', 'A file list program that supports multiple storage, powered by Gin and Solidjs.', 'Utilities', 'alist-alist-icon', '', 0, 'https://alist.nn.ci/'),
('allmapsoft-microsoftvirtualearthsatellite', 'Microsoft Virtualearth Satellite Downloader', 'This is a tool that can automatically download the Bing satellite maps images to your PC. It can download the small tiles and save them to your hard disk. After downloading, you can view the maps offline by its tool Maps Viewer.', 'Design', 'allmapsoft-microsoftvirtualearthsatellite-icon', '', 0, ''),
('allen&heath-ahmsystemmanager', 'AHM System Manager', 'AHM System Manager software and AHM-64’s flexible architecture allow rapid configuration, with no certified programming training required.', 'Development', 'allen&heath-ahmsystemmanager-icon', '', 0, ''),
('allen&heath-avantisdirector', 'Avantis Director', 'Avantis Director is a free Windows and Mac OS application enabling offline editing and online control capabilities. Offline mode can be used for the creation and editing of show files and system configuration, as well as serving as a training tool for new users. Online mode delivers full remote-control of the mixer, freeing the engineer from the mix position to make changes from anywhere in the venue.', 'Audio', 'allen&heath-avantisdirector-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.allen-heath.com/avantis'),
('allen&heath-customcontroleditor', 'Custom Control Editor', 'Custom Control Editor 1.1.1 Setup', 'Design', 'allen&heath-customcontroleditor-icon', '', 0, ''),
('allen&heath-dlivedirector', 'dLive Director', 'A multi-platform editor and control software for dLive. It lets you configure the system offline before the show, check and edit Show files from guest engineers, and control the mix live using a laptop or touch tablet. dLive Director has a touch-friendly interface, with resizable fader banks to suit different resolutions from pro tablets to large touch screens / all-in-ones. A Touchscreen view replicates every aspect of the dLive Surface GUI for instant familiarity to all dLive users.', 'Audio', 'allen&heath-dlivedirector-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.allen-heath.com/dlive-home/software');

INSERT INTO apps (id, name, description, category, icon, linux_alternative, popularity, homepage) VALUES
('allroundautomations-plsqldeveloper', 'PL/SQL Developer', 'PL/SQL Developer is an Integrated Development Environment for developing, testing, debugging and optimizing Oracle PL/SQL stored program units like packages, triggers and so on. PL/SQL Developer features context sensitive help and database object descriptions, syntax highlighting, data querying and editing, a graphical browser, and other functions to make a developer’s life easier.', 'Development', 'allroundautomations-plsqldeveloper-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.allroundautomations.com/products/pl-sql-developer/'),
('almico-speedfan', 'SpeedFan', 'SpeedFan is a program that monitors voltages, fan speeds and temperatures in computers with hardware monitor chips.', 'Utilities', 'almico-speedfan-icon', '', 0, ''),
('alphayama-poweriast', 'PowerIAST', 'Easily create diacritic letters to transliterate Sanskrit (and other Indian languages). Based on the PowerAccent project.', 'Utilities', 'alphayama-poweriast-icon', '', 0, ''),
('altdrag-altdrag', 'AltDrag', 'Easily drag windows when pressing the alt key', 'Utilities', 'altdrag-altdrag-icon', '', 0, 'https://stefansundin.github.io/altdrag/'),
('altsnap-altsnap', 'AltSnap', 'Easily drag windows when pressing the alt key. Unofficial fork of AltDrag from Stefan Sundin', 'Utilities', 'altsnap-altsnap-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/RamonUnch/AltSnap/wiki'),
('altap-salamander', 'Altap Salamander', 'Altap Salamander is a fast and reliable two-panel file manager for Windows. It has an intuitive interface, offers viewers for all popular file formats as well as support for common archives, and has built-in FTP and SFTP clients.', 'Utilities', 'altap-salamander-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.altap.cz'),
('amanharwara-altus', 'Altus', 'Desktop client for WhatsApp Web with themes & multiple account support.', 'Utilities', 'amanharwara-altus-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/amanharwara/altus'),
('amazon-awscli', 'AWS Command Line Interface', 'The AWS CLI is an open source tool built on top of the AWS SDK for Python (Boto) that provides commands for interacting with AWS services. With minimal configuration, you can start using all of the functionality provided by the AWS Management Console from your favorite terminal program.', 'Development', 'amazon-awscli-icon', '', 0, 'https://aws.amazon.com/cli/'),
('amazon-awsvpnclient', 'AWS VPN Client', 'Securely access AWS resources and resources in your on-premises network.', 'Utilities', 'amazon-awsvpnclient-icon', '', 0, ''),
('amazon-chime', 'Amazon Chime', 'Amazon Chime is a communications service that lets you meet, chat, and place business calls inside and outside your organization, all using a single application.', 'Development', 'amazon-chime-icon', '', 0, 'https://aws.amazon.com/chime'),
('amazon-corretto-11', 'Amazon Corretto 11', 'Amazon Corretto is a no-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK). Corretto comes with long-term support that will include performance enhancements and security fixes. Amazon runs Corretto internally on thousands of production services and Corretto is certified as compatible with the Java SE standard. With Corretto, you can develop and run Java applications on popular operating systems, including Linux, Windows, and macOS.', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-11-icon', '', 0, 'https://docs.aws.amazon.com/corretto/index.html'),
('amazon-corretto-17', 'Amazon Corretto 17', 'Amazon Corretto is a no-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK). Corretto comes with long-term support that will include performance enhancements and security fixes. Amazon runs Corretto internally on thousands of production services and Corretto is certified as compatible with the Java SE standard. With Corretto, you can develop and run Java applications on popular operating systems, including Linux, Windows, and macOS.', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-17-icon', '', 0, 'https://aws.amazon.com/corretto'),
('amazon-corretto-18', 'Amazon Corretto 18', 'Amazon Corretto is a no-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK). Corretto comes with long-term support that will include performance enhancements and security fixes. Amazon runs Corretto internally on thousands of production services and Corretto is certified as compatible with the Java SE standard. With Corretto, you can develop and run Java applications on popular operating systems, including Linux, Windows, and macOS.', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-18-icon', '', 0, 'https://docs.aws.amazon.com/corretto/index.html'),
('amazon-corretto-19', 'Amazon Corretto 19', 'Amazon Corretto is a no-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK). Corretto comes with long-term support that will include performance enhancements and security fixes. Amazon runs Corretto internally on thousands of production services and Corretto is certified as compatible with the Java SE standard. With Corretto, you can develop and run Java applications on popular operating systems, including Linux, Windows, and macOS.', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-19-icon', '', 0, 'https://docs.aws.amazon.com/corretto/index.html'),
('amazon-corretto-8', 'Amazon Corretto 8', 'No-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK).', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-8-icon', '', 0, 'https://docs.aws.amazon.com/corretto/index.html'),
('amazon-games', 'Amazon Games', 'Amazon Games app is a Windows PC game launcher that allows you to claim, download, and play new and classic Windows PC games every month from Prime Gaming.', 'Games', 'amazon-games-icon', '', 0, 'https://gaming.amazon.com/home'),
('amazon-kindle', 'Amazon Kindle', 'The Kindle app is available for most major smartphones, tablets and computers. That means with our free Kindle reading apps, you can buy a Kindle book once, and read it on any device with the Kindle app installed*. You can also read that same Kindle book on a Kindle device if you own one.', 'Design', 'amazon-kindle-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.amazon.com/kindle-dbs/fd/kcp'),
('amazon-nosqlworkbench', 'NoSQL Workbench', 'NoSQL Workbench is a unified visual IDE tool that provides data modeling, data visualization, and query development features to help you design, create, query, and manage DynamoDB tables.', 'Development', 'amazon-nosqlworkbench-icon', '', 0, ''),
('amazon-opensearch-odbc', 'OpenSearch SQL ODBC Driver', 'OpenSearchODBC is a read-only ODBC driver for Windows and Mac for connecting to OpenSearch SQL support.', 'Development', 'amazon-opensearch-odbc-icon', '', 0, ''),
('amazon-sam-cli', 'AWS SAM Command Line Interface', 'The AWS Serverless Application Model (SAM) is an open-source framework for building serverless applications.', 'Utilities', 'amazon-sam-cli-icon', '', 0, 'https://aws.amazon.com/serverless/sam/'),
('amazon-sendtokindle', 'Amazon Send to Kindle', 'Send to Kindle will appear when you right click on a file in Windows Explorer or in the print dialog of any Windows application. To send multiple documents to Kindle without opening them, simply select documents and choose Send to Kindle from the right-click menu in Windows Explorer. You can download archived personal documents from any Kindle device or using the free reading app on your iOS or Android device. Whispersync of notes, highlights, bookmarks and last page read is available on your archived personal documents that have been converted into Kindle format.', 'Office', 'amazon-sendtokindle-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.amazon.com/gp/sendtokindle'),
('amazon-sessionmanagerplugin', 'Session Manager Plugin', 'This plugin helps you to use the AWS Command Line Interface (AWS CLI) to start and end sessions to your managed instances.', 'Design', 'amazon-sessionmanagerplugin-icon', '', 0, ''),
('amazon-workspacesclient', 'Amazon WorkSpaces', 'Amazon WorkSpaces offers an easy way to provide a cloud-based desktop experience to your end users.', 'Development', 'amazon-workspacesclient-icon', '', 0, 'https://clients.amazonworkspaces.com/'),
('aminemouafik-ferdi', 'Ferdi', 'Ferdi is a desktop app that helps you organize how you use your favourite apps by combining them into one application. It is based on Franz - a software already used by thousands of people - with the difference that Ferdi gives you many additional features and doesn''t restrict its usage! Ferdi is compatible with your existing Franz account so you can continue right where you left off. Find out more about Ferdi and its features on getferdi.com.', 'Social', 'aminemouafik-ferdi-icon', '', 0, 'https://getferdi.com/'),
('anaconda-anaconda3', 'Anaconda3', 'Anaconda Individual Edition is the easiest way to perform Python/R data science and machine learning on a single machine. Developed for solo practitioners, it is the toolkit that equips you to work with thousands of open-source packages and libraries.', 'Development', 'anaconda-anaconda3-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.anaconda.com/products/individual'),
('anaconda-miniconda3', 'Miniconda3', 'Miniconda is a free minimal installer for conda. It is a small, bootstrap version of Anaconda that includes only conda, Python, the packages they depend on, and a small number of other useful packages, including pip, zlib and a few others.', 'Utilities', 'anaconda-miniconda3-icon', '', 0, 'https://docs.conda.io/en/latest/miniconda.html'),
('andrewiethoff-exactaudiocopy', 'Exact Audio Copy', 'Exact Audio Copy is a so-called audio grabber for audio CDs using standard CD and DVD-ROM drives.', 'Audio', 'andrewiethoff-exactaudiocopy-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.exactaudiocopy.de/en/'),
('andreaswascher-repoz', 'RepoZ', 'RepoZ is a zero-conf git repository hub with Windows Explorer & CLI-enhancements.', 'Development', 'andreaswascher-repoz-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/awaescher/RepoZ'),
('andresmorelos-invoncify', 'Invoncify', 'Flexible invoicing desktop app with beautiful & customizable templates', 'Social', 'andresmorelos-invoncify-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/AndresMorelos/Invoncify'),
('andrewzhezherun-windjview', 'WinDjView', 'WinDjView is a fast, compact and powerful DjVu viewer for Windows with tabbed interface, continuous scrolling and advanced printing options.', 'Utilities', 'andrewzhezherun-windjview-icon', '', 0, ''),
('angusjohnson-pdftkbuilder', 'PDFTK Builder', 'Take control of your PDF documents - merge or split pages; stamp pages or add background watermarks; add page numbers; and even rotate pages.', 'Office', 'angusjohnson-pdftkbuilder-icon', '', 0, ''),
('angusjohnson-resourcehacker', 'Resource Hacker', 'Resource Hacker is a program that allows you to compile and decompile various resources and file types.', 'Development', 'angusjohnson-resourcehacker-icon', '', 0, 'http://www.angusj.com/resourcehacker/'),
('anjok07-ultimatevocalremover', 'Ultimate Vocal Remover', 'This application uses state-of-the-art source separation models to remove vocals from audio files. UVR''s core developers trained all of the models provided in this package (except for the Demucs v3 4-stem models).', 'Development', 'anjok07-ultimatevocalremover-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/Anjok07/ultimatevocalremovergui'),
('anki-anki', 'Anki', 'Anki is a program which makes remembering things easy.
Because it''s a lot more efficient than traditional study methods, you can either greatly decrease your time spent studying, or greatly increase the amount you learn.
Anyone who needs to remember things in their daily life can benefit from Anki.
Since it is content-agnostic and supports images, audio, videos and scientific markup (via LaTeX), the possibilities are endless.', 'Development', 'anki-anki-icon', '', 0, 'https://apps.ankiweb.net/'),
('antsoftware-antrenamer', 'Ant Renamer', 'Ant Renamer is a free program that makes easier the renaming of lots of files and folders by using specified settings. It supports Unicode names.', 'Development', 'antsoftware-antrenamer-icon', '', 0, 'https://antp.be/software/renamer'),
('anthonybeaumont-achievementwatcher', 'Achievement Watcher', 'Achievement Watcher allows you to view every achievement earned on your PC whether it''s coming from Steam, a Steam emulator, and more.', 'Games', 'anthonybeaumont-achievementwatcher-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/xan105/Achievement-Watcher'),
('antimicro-antimicro', 'AntiMicro', 'Graphical program used to map keyboard buttons and mouse controls to a gamepad. Useful for playing games with no gamepad support', 'Games', 'antimicro-antimicro-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/AntiMicro/antimicro'),
('antimicrox-antimicrox', 'AntiMicroX', 'Graphical program used to map keyboard buttons and mouse controls to a gamepad. Useful for playing games with no gamepad support.', 'Games', 'antimicrox-antimicrox-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/AntiMicroX/antimicrox'),
('antimicrox-antimicroxportable', 'AntiMicroX Portable', 'Graphical program used to map keyboard buttons and mouse controls to a gamepad. Useful for playing games with no gamepad support.', 'Games', 'antimicrox-antimicroxportable-icon', '', 0, ''),
('antibodysoftware-bulkimagedownloader', 'Bulk Image Downloader', 'Bulk Image Downloader (BID) is a simple to use yet powerful image downloading tool for Windows PCs.', 'Design', 'antibodysoftware-bulkimagedownloader-icon', '', 0, 'https://bulkimagedownloader.com/'),
('antibodysoftware-wizfile', 'WizFile', 'Find files by name on your hard drives almost instantly.', 'Utilities', 'antibodysoftware-wizfile-icon', '', 0, 'https://antibody-software.com/wizfile/'),
('antibodysoftware-wizkey', 'WizKey', 'WizKey is a keyboard enhancement utility that makes the typing of accented and other special characters easy. The most common characters can be typed using easy to remember keyboard shortcuts, and less common characters can be selected and searched for by code or name using the built in Unicode character browser.', 'Development', 'antibodysoftware-wizkey-icon', '', 0, 'https://antibody-software.com/web/software/software/wizkey-makes-it-easy-to-type-accented-and-other-special-unicode-characters/'),
('antibodysoftware-wizmouse', 'WizMouse', 'WizMouse is a mouse enhancement utility that makes your mouse wheel work on the window currently under the mouse pointer, instead of the currently focused window. This means you no longer have to click on a window before being able to scroll it with the mouse wheel.', 'Utilities', 'antibodysoftware-wizmouse-icon', '', 0, 'https://antibody-software.com/web/software/software/wizmouse-makes-your-mouse-wheel-work-on-the-window-under-the-mouse/'),
('antibodysoftware-wiztree', 'WizTree', 'WizTree is a hard drive disk space analyser similar to WinDirStat but is MUCH faster.', 'Utilities', 'antibodysoftware-wiztree-icon', '', 0, 'https://diskanalyzer.com'),
('antoineaflalo-soundswitch', 'SoundSwitch', 'No more navigating through several menus and screens. Just configure SoundSwitch once - and you are able to switch between your devices as fast as never before!', 'Audio', 'antoineaflalo-soundswitch-icon', '', 0, 'https://soundswitch.aaflalo.me/'),
