('acrosync-duplicacyweb', 'Duplicacy Web Edition', 'This version can be used without a license if you only need the restore, check, copy, and prune operations. If you do need to run backups, a fully functional 30-day trial license will be automatically downloaded to enable the backup operation. After 30 days, a personal or commercial license can be purchased.', 'Utilities', 'acrosync-duplicacyweb-icon', '', 0, 'https://duplicacy.com/'),
