('ajeetdsouza-zoxide', 'zoxide', 'zoxide is a smarter cd command, inspired by z and autojump. It remembers which directories you use most frequently, so you can "jump" to them in just a few keystrokes. zoxide works on all major shells.', 'Development', 'ajeetdsouza-zoxide-icon', '', 0, 'https://github.com/ajeetdsouza/zoxide'),
