('alexx2000-doublecommander', 'Double Commander', 'Double Commander is a cross platform open source file manager with two panels side by side. It is inspired by Total Commander and features some new ideas.', 'Development', 'alexx2000-doublecommander-icon', '', 0, 'https://doublecmd.sourceforge.io'),
