- Much more!', 'Design', 'binarymark-batchdocs-icon', '', 0, 'https://www.binarymark.com/products/bulk-document-processor?ref=winget'),
('binarymark-batchencodingconverter', 'Batch Encoding Converter Free Edition', 'Convert 1000s of files between more than 100 text encodings and binary formats: Unicode, ANSI, Latin, Cyrillic, ASCII, UTF8, ISO, OEM, Mac, Base-64, Bin-Hex, Quoted-Printable.
